Method Detail

setOperation

public void setOperation(int operation)
Sets the operation for this filter list. If set to AND, only Attributes which pass through ALL filters contained within will be returned. If set to OR, Attributes which pass through ANY of the contained filters will be returned.

Parameters:
operation - the operation to use for this filter.
